from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error # 均方误差
from sklearn.linear_model import SGDRegressor

问题（1）¶

以2℃作为间隔（步长），画出该种热敏电阻在温度范围为0℃~100℃间阻值随温度变化的特性曲线。

In [4]:
t = []
R = []
for i in range(0,101,2):
    t.append(i)
    temp = 22 * np.exp(3100 * (1 / (273.15 + i) - 1 / (273.15 + 25)))
    R.append(temp)

# 画图
plt.figure()
plt.figure(figsize=(5,5))
plt.plot(t, R) 
plt.xlabel('t/℃')
plt.ylabel('R/kΩ')
plt.title('热敏电阻阻值随温度变化的特性曲线',fontproperties='SimHei')
plt.show()

问题（2）¶

2.1 在（1）中获得的20℃-80℃范围的数据上添加适当噪声（以零均值、标准偏差取500的高斯噪声为例），用添加噪声后的数据模拟实验数据；
2.2 用模拟的实验数据作为训练数据集，采用曲线拟合最小二乘法分别获得模型阶次n=1,2,3,4,5,6时传感器特性曲线对应的多项式模型；
2.3 分别计算不同阶次模型在温度范围20℃-80℃（训练集）上和温度范围0℃~100℃刨除20℃-80℃温度范围后（测试集）上的误差（均方误差, mean squared error），观察训练集和测试集上误差随模型阶次的变化规律并加以讨论。

问题（3）¶

3）重复（2）相应内容10次（每次重新添加噪声模拟不同批次实验数据），观察并讨论由于采用不同训练数据给拟合（学习）结果带来的影响；

# n = 1,2,3,4,5,6   
# 每个阶次重复10次实验
train_MSE_500 = np.zeros([10,6])
test_MSE_500  = np.zeros([10,6])
for i in range(10):
    # 划分训练集和验证集
    x_train = t[list.index(t,20):list.index(t,80)+1] # 包含20和80
    y_train = R[list.index(t,20):list.index(t,80)+1] 
    x_test  = t[:list.index(t,20)] + t[list.index(t,80)+1:]
    y_test  = R[:list.index(t,20)] + R[list.index(t,80)+1:]
    # 取高斯噪声
    noise = list(np.random.normal(loc = 0, scale = 0.5, size = len(y_train)))
    # 训练集加入噪声
    y_train = [y_train[i] + noise[i] for i in range(len(y_train))]
    
    # 最小二乘法拟合
    x_train = [[x_train[i]] for i in range(len(x_train))]
    y_train = [[y_train[i]] for i in range(len(y_train))]
    x_test  = [[x_test[i]]  for i in range(len(x_test))]
    y_test  = [[y_test[i]]  for i in range(len(y_test))]
    for n in range(1,7,1):
        # 多项式模型训练和预测
        model = pipeline.make_pipeline(PolynomialFeatures(n),LinearRegression())
        model.fit(x_train,y_train)
        p_train = model.predict(x_train)
        p_test  = model.predict(x_test)
        if i == 1:
            # 画图
            plt.figure()
            plt.figure(figsize=(5,5))
            xx = x_test[:a]+x_train+x_test[a:]
            p_train = list(p_train)
            p_test = list(p_test)
            yy = p_test[:a]+p_train+p_test[a:]
            plt.plot(t,R,label='R_true')
            plt.plot(xx,yy,label='R_pred')
            plt.legend()
            plt.xlabel('n')
            plt.ylabel('MSE')
            plt.title('多项式模型拟合结果, n = %d'% n, fontproperties='SimHei')
            fig = plt.gcf()
            plt.show()
            name = "q2_ans"+str(n)+".png"
            fig.savefig(name)
        # MSE计算
        train_MSE_500[i][n-1] = mean_squared_error(y_train,p_train)
        test_MSE_500[i][n-1]  = mean_squared_error(y_test,p_test)

# n = 1,2,3,4,5,6   
# 每个阶次重复10次实验
# 取3组不同的噪声强度（加问题（2）（3）共四组）

train_MSE = np.zeros([4,10,6])
test_MSE  = np.zeros([4,10,6])
train_MSE[1] = train_MSE_500
test_MSE[1]  = test_MSE_500
for i in range(10):
    sgm_cnt = 0
    for sgm in [0.1,1,10]:
        # 划分训练集和验证集
        x_train = t[list.index(t,20):list.index(t,80)+1] # 包含20和80
        y_train = R[list.index(t,20):list.index(t,80)+1] 
        x_test  = t[:list.index(t,20)] + t[list.index(t,80)+1:]
        y_test  = R[:list.index(t,20)] + R[list.index(t,80)+1:]
        # 取高斯噪声
        noise = list(np.random.normal(loc = 0, scale = sgm, size = len(y_train)))
        # 训练集加入噪声
        y_train = [y_train[i] + noise[i] for i in range(len(y_train))]
        
        # 最小二乘法拟合
        x_train = [[x_train[i]] for i in range(len(x_train))]
        y_train = [[y_train[i]] for i in range(len(y_train))]
        x_test  = [[x_test[i]]  for i in range(len(x_test))]
        y_test  = [[y_test[i]]  for i in range(len(y_test))]
        for n in range(1,7,1):
            # 多项式模型训练和预测
            model = pipeline.make_pipeline(PolynomialFeatures(n),LinearRegression())
            model.fit(x_train,y_train)
            p_train = model.predict(x_train)
            p_test  = model.predict(x_test)
            # MSE计算
            train_MSE[sgm_cnt][i][n-1] = mean_squared_error(y_train,p_train)
            test_MSE[sgm_cnt][i][n-1]  = mean_squared_error(y_test,p_test)

        if sgm_cnt == 0:
            sgm_cnt += 2
        else:
            sgm_cnt += 1

            a = list.index(t,30)
            xx = x_test[:a]+x_train+x_test[a:]
            p_train = list(p_train)
            p_test = list(p_test)
            yy = p_test[:a]+p_train+p_test[a:]
            plt.plot(t,R,label='R_true')
            plt.plot(xx,yy,label='R_pred')
            plt.legend()
            plt.xlabel('n')
            plt.ylabel('MSE')
            plt.title('多项式模型拟合结果, n = %d'% n, fontproperties='SimHei')
            fig = plt.gcf()
            plt.show()
            name = "q5_ans_n"+str(n)+"_3070.png"
            fig.savefig(name)
        # MSE计算
        train_MSE_500[i][n-1] = mean_squared_error(y_train,p_train)
        test_MSE_500[i][n-1]  = mean_squared_error(y_test,p_test)

# 划分训练集和验证集
x_train = t[list.index(t,20):list.index(t,80)+1] # 包含20和80
y_train = R[list.index(t,20):list.index(t,80)+1] 
x_test  = t[:list.index(t,20)] + t[list.index(t,80)+1:]
y_test  = R[:list.index(t,20)] + R[list.index(t,80)+1:]
# 取高斯噪声
noise = list(np.random.normal(loc = 0, scale = 0.5, size = len(y_train)))
# 训练集加入噪声
y_train = [y_train[i] + noise[i] for i in range(len(y_train))]

# 变形
x_train_new = [[1 / (item + 273.15)] for item in x_train]
y_train_new = [[np.log(item)] for item in y_train]
x_test_new = [[1 / (item + 273.15)] for item in x_test]
plt.plot(x_train_new,y_train_new)
plt.xlabel('1 / t + 273.15')
plt.ylabel('lnR')
fig = plt.gcf()
plt.show()
name = "q7_2"+".png"
fig.savefig(name)
# 线性回归
model = LinearRegression().fit(x_train_new, y_train_new)

y_train_pred = model.predict(x_train_new)
y_train_pred = np.exp(y_train_pred)
y_test_pred = model.predict(x_test_new)
y_test_pred = np.exp(y_test_pred)

# 拟合直线
k = model.coef_[0][0]
para = model.intercept_[0]
